" ~/.vimrc - minimal Vim setup for FreeBSD driver work
"
" Companion for Chapter 2, section "Configuring Vim for Syntax
" Highlighting". Copy this to ~/.vimrc (note the leading dot, which
" is not legal in this repository's filenames, hence the "dot-vimrc"
" name here).

syntax on
set number
set tabstop=8
set shiftwidth=8
set autoindent
set background=dark
